
--------------------------------User calls-----------------------------------------

Get All Users(GET)	: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/User/

Get User By ID(GET) : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/User/{id}

Add User(POST)		: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/User/add

Delete User(DEL)	: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/User/delete/{id}

--------------------------------Interview details calls--------------------------------------

Get All Interview Details(GET)					: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/

Get count of Interview Details(GET)				: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/count

Get Interview Details By ID(GET) 				: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/{id}

Get Interview by Interviewer and interview name : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/{interviewerName}/{interviewName}

Add Interview Details(POST)						: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/add

Delete Intervew Details(DEL)					: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/delete/{id}

Get Interview Details by interviewer Name(GET)  : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/InterviewerName/{name}

Get Interview Details by interview Name(GET)    : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/InterviewName/{name}

Update interview details status on fly(PUT)		: http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/Interview/UpdateStatus/{id}/{Status}


---------------------------------Interview Attendee Calls -----------------------------------------------

Get All Interview Attendee(GET) 			 	   : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/

Get Total interviews(GET) 		 			 	   : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/interviewscount

Add Attendee to interview(POST)	 			 	   : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/add/{interviewId}/{userID}

Get Attendee by Interview ID(GET)				   : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/Interview/{id}

Get Attendee by User ID(GET)	 				   : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/User/{id}

Get No of Interviews attended by user by id 	   :  http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/UserAttendCount/{id}

Get No of Interviews conducted for interview by id : http://localhost:9091/InterviewTracking/attendee/InterviewConductedCount/{id}

User record format to add

{
    "firstName": "Test Firstname",
    "lastName": "Test Last Name",
    "email": "test@gmail.com",
    "mobile": "9215648999"
}

Interview record Format to add

{
      "interviewerName": "Interviewer for C sharp",
        "interviewName": "C sharp",
        "userSkills": "C sharp",
        "interviewStatus": "Passed",
        "remarks": "Proceed for further rounds"
}





